
## Setup

### Packages
Install relevant R packages - we need to make a requirements.txt or similar (depends what R uses) - so anyone can get started with our application - potentially have a look to see if R has virtual environments (could be useful)

### OpenAQ Setup
Please create a .Renviron file in your local directory which will be used to store your API key in the form:

```
OPEN_AQ_API_KEY = [YOUR API KEY]
```

To create API Key please sign-up at OpenAQ: https://docs.openaq.org/using-the-api/api-key
